name: Jaipur my soul
short_description:
Jaipur the capital city of Rajasthan also known as Paris of India is not only famous for its rich heritage of culture it also includes bewitching and splendid vibrant colors of the excursions located in this place. The amazing and stunning beatiful visit to Pink city captures the mood of visitors and lure the sight of onlookers everytime.

This fantabulous city is not only famous for its eye catching and well build monuments, historical forts, buildings, lush gardens and religious shrines but also for  shops, restaurents, shopping acarde, hotels and disco thec.

Let your imagination loose in the place that has endless serenity and endless amusement for visitors. This fun filled and sparkling destination provides all adventures that everyone wants to have to accomplish the wishes to have mesmerizing trip at the city beautiful.
